Darkwing tried to maneuver from the great jaws but they landed on 
the tip of a wing, ripping it to shreds.  Darkwing began falling 
towards the water below.  

Dreadwind, saw the thing, not caring he shot two rockets at 
Ragnus's eye before descending for his buddy.
